title: steps of the trickster
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

These shoes allow you to freely change the sound of your steps when you wear them. Doing this doesn't change their volume, but you can make them sound as though the shoes are made from a different material. For example, your steps can sound like bare feet, sharp heels, or metal boots.